Ama-Tsu-Mara is god of blacksmiths and weaponsmiths in the Japanese Pantheon. He appears as a massive human.
Ama-Tsu-Mara dwells with the Gnomish Pantheon in the Golden Hills in Dothion, Bytopia, sharing the Mithral Forge with Flandal Steelskin. He is of neutral alignment.  His sacred animal is the badger. His clerics wear leather caps and vests. 

